And the JavaScript (in script.js file):

```javascript
const form = document.querySelector('form');
const wishElement = document.getElementById('wish');

form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const name = document.getElementById('name').value;
    const age = document.getElementById('age').value;
    const wish = `Happy ${age}th birthday, ${name}!`;
    wishElement.textContent = wish;
});
```

This code creates a basic birthday web application with a form to input the name and age, and a section to display the birthday wish. The application is responsive and visually appealing, with a modern design.
